        <srccitea>USGS ECSTD</srccitea>
        <srccontr>Critical stress threshold values were calculated from surface sediment texture data found in the U.S. Geological Survey East-Coast Sediment Texture Database.  Only those data points with the full phi grain size distribution (totalling to 95-105% of the sediment sample) were used.</srccontr>
